dc_title_s: Map of the states of Indiana, and Ohio, with part of Michigan Territory.
dc_description_s: Shows counties, roads, populated places, and water features. Washington and Greenwich prime meridians. Inset: "Plan of Cincinnati." Engraved and printed by Fenner Sears  Co. 1 map; 23 x 38 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Hinton, Isaac Taylor, 1799-1847.,Fenner Sears  Co.,Simpkin, Marshall and Co.
